      "title": "一...就... — As soon as...then...",
      "explanation": "一 + Verb1 + 就 + Verb2 means 'as soon as [action 1] happens, [action 2] immediately follows'. The two actions are tightly connected in time. Subject can be the same or different. This pattern implies immediate consequence or habitual succession.",
