      "explanation": "不管/无论 + condition + 都/也 + result: expresses that the result is true regardless of the condition. 不管 and 无论 both mean 'no matter'; 无论 is slightly more formal and literary. The condition clause often contains question words (什么, 怎么, 谁, 哪里). 都 is most common in the result; 也 is also used.",
